{"tid":1671732,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"U生活 【以假亂真】iPhone X一秒變iPhone 11 淘寶熱賣神奇「鏡頭貼紙」","createTime":"2019-10-23T16:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T12:22:14.000Z","uid":219147,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9fe5feaa5fee2e7092a78b60fbb67ecccc298b","tid":1671732,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:09:28.000Z","msg":"人要make up，機都要up&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n蘋果今年新推出的iPhone 11系列，在外形上相較前一代最大不同就是後置鏡頭，其中iPhone 11 Pro及iPhone Pro Max都用了方框包住「三鏡」的設計。不少蘋果粉絲都覺得這個設計很難看，但從好的方面看，這個設計識別度卻很高，和前代有所區分，這樣至少可以讓別人看得出你買了新手機。<br />\n<br />\n不過iPhone 11 pro系列售價不太平民，很多買了iPhone X系列的人都不捨得換機。不換機但又想裝作換了機，應該怎麼辦，在淘寶就能找到答案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JYOhb3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJYOhb3f.png&h=497872af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上圖片<br />\n自從iPhone 11系列發佈，淘寶就出現了一款貼紙產品，這種貼紙仿照iPhone 11新的鏡頭設計，可以貼在iPhone 11的鏡頭上，保護突出的鏡頭防止刮花磨損。另外還有一種鏡頭貼紙可以貼在iPhone X上，讓X「一秒升呢」偽裝成iPhone 11或iPhone 11 pro。<br />\n<br />\n售賣類似產品的淘寶店，最高交易量都有十幾萬，看來購買的人也不少。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aiShWvw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaiShWvw.png&h=6f814249&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42itiJS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42itiJS.png&h=bb9b0ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n有網友批評&mdash;&mdash;人類為了面子，什麼發明都做得出來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪姐係裝假狗 <br />\n自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a2799792fb94930f99a234380edbabd7513e5b","tid":1671732,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-2